body:
### Who We Are
We are Ratchet Robotics (team 6806). We have a strong engineering and programming focus,
and enjoy using CAD, CAM, CNC tools, 3D printers, and other advanced machining tools.
We are a team under the auspices of [BadgerBOTS](http://www.badgerbots.org), and interact with other
local spaces such as [Sector67](http://www.sector67.org).
